      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "To draft a response, I'll prioritize addressing Marcus' concerns and emotions while using empathetic language. Here's a suggested reply:\n\n\"Dear Marcus, \n\nI'm deeply sorry to hear that SkyLink's 6-hour delay caused you to miss your sister's wedding rehearsal. I can only imagine the distress and disappointment this must have caused you. I want to assure you that we are committed to making things right. A full refund is being processed immediately, and we're taking steps to prevent similar delays in the future.\n\nRegarding compensation for emotional distress, I understand the significance of this event and want to offer a gesture of goodwill. Please let me know if there's anything else I can do to support you during this time.\n\nSincerely, [Your Name].\"\n\nThis response acknowledges Marcus' emotions, offers a tangible solution, and provides a clarity on the support offered. These elements should help de-escalate the situation and give the automated sentiment score a more positive reading.",
